      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys) with documented verification test suite; FDA-internal solver subject to agency SQA procedures; version control and audit trail maintained for all simulation runs.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 employed with vendor-supplied verification and validation documentation. FDA-internal solver operates under 21 CFR Part 11-compliant SQA framework. DePuy Synthes simulation environment covered by ISO 13485 design-control procedures. All three ensemble members satisfy Gradation 2 SQA requirements."
