      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario geometry, loading, and boundary conditions are representative of the COU; any extrapolation from validation to COU is bounded and justified.",
      "rationale": "Validation activity uses the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry, F1717 fixture, and loading protocol as the COU. No geometric or loading extrapolation required. Multi-laboratory design (FDA + industry) strengthens external validity. Validation activity relevance rated Gradation 3."
    }
